HEADWORD: Hallucinator
<hw>Hal*lu"ci*na`tor</hw>
<pr>(h⟦acr⟧l*l⟦umac⟧"s⟦icr⟧*n⟦amac⟧`t⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
